Appears to be the same as ZUCZUG 1 Gang.  

To flash I needed to power up the device without GPIO0 low; put GPIO0 low then briefly put RST to low.  Otherwise would not flash.
Pads across the top to flash, looking left to right (with writing correct way up): 3V3, RX, TX, GPIO0, RST, GND